I've spent the last 3 weeks playing with this tiny but oh so powerful little drone, DJI Mini 3 Pro. It fits in my pocket but still shoots incredible well and even handle the Icelandic winds. It's seriously impressive that 249g drone can shoot 4k in 50fps and stay in the air for 34 minutes!
It's been so fun to be back in Iceland and out flying drones again and now summer is almost here. Can't wait for more adventures 🙂
